    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事背景</strong></h2>《转厝》是一款中国本土题材的2d横板卷轴恐怖悬疑解谜游戏。生活在南部渔村的女主角安珍为了寻找失踪的弟弟，受指引孤身一人踏上传说中的土地，通过多主角模式的探索以及互动，被遗忘的真相逐步展露出全貌。多年前的火灾、村民诡异的神情、遗落的书报、奇怪的习俗以及无处不在被奉为至高的福鱼，一切都指向这里的神秘组织、村民口中至高无上的万苍会。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/bde0966f0173bf2db759374ffee88b19.poster.avif?t=1769758183\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/bde0966f0173bf2db759374ffee88b19.webm?t=1769758183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/bde0966f0173bf2db759374ffee88b19.mp4?t=1769758183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>剧情</strong></h2>这是一场离奇、诡异又险象环生的寻亲之旅。跟随主角安珍的步伐，透过不同时空和人物的角度，揭开月岛上被千丝万缕缠绕住的真相。<br>这也是一个充满着东方特色的现实主义故事，你可能会在这跨越百年的纠葛中，看到似曾相识的影子。<br>精巧多元的叙事结构让你在悬疑和真相间浮沉，仿佛触手可及又隔着挥之不去的厚纱……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/7f97686c67b6d598eb505e01d3ebc95a.poster.avif?t=1769758183\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/7f97686c67b6d598eb505e01d3ebc95a.webm?t=1769758183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/7f97686c67b6d598eb505e01d3ebc95a.mp4?t=1769758183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/1deab755a8d5b25bf0b1e0ff6db09b66.poster.avif?t=1769758183\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/1deab755a8d5b25bf0b1e0ff6db09b66.webm?t=1769758183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/1deab755a8d5b25bf0b1e0ff6db09b66.mp4?t=1769758183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索</strong></h2>控制主角安珍与另一神秘人物进行收集和互动，一步步踏入秘密的核心，感受重重反转与“真相“的颠覆。<br> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/500b7b1eb77a16a75f129f0b4ba767df.poster.avif?t=1769758183\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/500b7b1eb77a16a75f129f0b4ba767df.webm?t=1769758183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/500b7b1eb77a16a75f129f0b4ba767df.mp4?t=1769758183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/27c4a53ae6412118a433936b0d7abb3a.poster.avif?t=1769758183\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/27c4a53ae6412118a433936b0d7abb3a.webm?t=1769758183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/27c4a53ae6412118a433936b0d7abb3a.mp4?t=1769758183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>解谜</strong></h2>根据场景和剧情特别打造的解谜小游戏，高度还原贴合现实感受，绝无仅有的代入感，富有趣味又不会无情卡关。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/8bff38df1cf0da59f49f97f56388c107.poster.avif?t=1769758183\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/8bff38df1cf0da59f49f97f56388c107.webm?t=1769758183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/8bff38df1cf0da59f49f97f56388c107.mp4?t=1769758183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/d8c71d013894034319489635cafdbf9c.poster.avif?t=1769758183\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/d8c71d013894034319489635cafdbf9c.webm?t=1769758183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/d8c71d013894034319489635cafdbf9c.mp4?t=1769758183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> 游戏特色</strong></h2>资深音乐制作人精心定制大量原创音乐，高度贴合每个场景与剧情节奏。<br>丰富的道具和谜题设置完美贴合海量场景剧情，深度还原时代和地方特色。<br>自由探索贴近现实生活的中式场景，增加代入感与角色的共情。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/665f95efe4a392fb5a63ce626109516e.poster.avif?t=1769758183\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/665f95efe4a392fb5a63ce626109516e.webm?t=1769758183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/665f95efe4a392fb5a63ce626109516e.mp4?t=1769758183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/34b3393812bb81b75254c03838749e9b.poster.avif?t=1769758183\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/34b3393812bb81b75254c03838749e9b.webm?t=1769758183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/34b3393812bb81b75254c03838749e9b.mp4?t=1769758183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> 游戏风格</strong></h2>民俗手绘风格；大量漫画以及动画演出；海量场景与原创音乐；<br>以闽南语为主的多种语言配音100%还原真实感，原声音轨。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/b84fb45ced5e3e34d229736aaa56885b.poster.avif?t=1769758183\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/b84fb45ced5e3e34d229736aaa56885b.webm?t=1769758183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285270/extras/b84fb45ced5e3e34d229736aaa56885b.mp4?t=1769758183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>[/url]",
